{"id":443807,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Antoni_Opolski","text":"Antoni Opolski (11 June 1913 \u2013 17 March 2014) was a Polish physicist. His field was astronomy and astrophysics. After World War II, he worked at the astronomical observatory of the University of Wroc\u0142aw. He retired in 1983. He was born in Rozwad\u00F3w (now Lviv Oblast, Ukraine).\nOpolski died from natural causes on 17 March 2014 in Wroc\u0142aw, Poland. He was 100 years old. His funeral was held on 22 March.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Poles","surface_form":"Polish","offset":52},{"uri":"Physicist","surface_form":"physicist","offset":59},{"uri":"Astronomy","surface_form":"astronomy","offset":84},{"uri":"Astrophysics","surface_form":"astrophysics","offset":98},{"uri":"World_War_II","surface_form":"World War II","offset":118},{"uri":"University_of_Wroc%C5%82aw","surface_form":"University of Wroc\u0142aw","offset":181},{"uri":"Rozwad%C3%B3w","surface_form":"Rozwad\u00F3w","offset":239},{"uri":"Lviv_Oblast","surface_form":"Lviv Oblast","offset":253},{"uri":"Ukraine","surface_form":"Ukraine","offset":266},{"uri":"Natural_causes","surface_form":"natural causes","offset":294},{"uri":"Wroc%C5%82aw","surface_form":"Wroc\u0142aw","offset":329},{"uri":"Poland","surface_form":"Poland","offset":338},{"uri":"Funeral","surface_form":"funeral","offset":372}]}